features: Get organized with style with our Classic Chic file folders, a pack of 6 folders in striking colors and patterns
These letter-size (8 1/2" x 11") tabbed file folders measure 11.5” by 9.5”, and are great for home and office use
Left position, center position and right position allow you to choose the way you file, with tabs for easy labeling
Modern fashion prints add a touch of style to any office environment; this set includes gray, pink and blue folders with gold foil details
Inspire your best work with patterns and designs that reflect your taste and personality
body.description: File in style with U Brands 6 pack Classic Chic fashion file folders. The exteriors of these folders evoke a sense of preparedness and professionalism, featuring gold foil details on gray, pink and blue. With 6 folders in total, they allow you to organize your papers by type so you can easily locate everything from work projects to family records and school assignments. Each letter-size folder measures 11.5” x 9.5” and has 1/3-cut tabs in assorted positions. Whether you're a student, a business person or a busy stay-at-home parent, they are the perfect solution. U Brands is a dynamic, new company focused on a complete and diverse line of stationery, office, and home goods. We are developing some of the most unique and inspiring stationery and home office products. Our pledge is to deliver innovative and creative designs with great quality and value.

reviews.reviewText: The folders themselves would have been fine, had they not been stuffed into a self-sealing envelope that was too small and bent them. This was not a delivery issue - but a manufacturer issue. I hope placing a heavy book on top will straighten them out.
